# Optional: point the frontend's /api/analyze and /api/extract routes at the
# Python backend. When set, analysis is proxied to FastAPI (so responses can
# carry real-LLM suggestions when that backend has OPENROUTER_API_KEY set), and
# PDF/DOCX file upload is enabled via the backend's /extract endpoint.
#
# When UNSET (the default), the app is fully self-contained: matching runs in
# the in-process TypeScript port (provider "mock") and file upload returns 501.
#
# No trailing slash.
# BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000
